{{Infobox dam | name = Marun Dam | name_official = | image = | image_size = | image_caption = | image_alt = | location_map = Iran | location_map_size = | location_map_caption = | location_map_alt = | coordinates = {{coord|30|42|36|N|50|21|54|E|type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | country = Iran | location = [[Behbahan]] in [[Behbahan County]], [[Khuzestan Province]] | purpose = Power, irrigation | status = O | construction_began = 1989 | opening = {{Start date and age|1998}} | demolished = | cost = | owner = | dam_type = Embankment, rock-fill | dam_crosses = [[Marun River]] | dam_length = {{Convert|340|m|ft|abbr=on}} | dam_height = | dam_height_foundation= {{Convert|175|m|ft|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Marun Reservoir Dam and Power Plant|url=http://www.peyab.org/maruneng.htm|publisher=Peyab Sazeh Gostar Co.|accessdate=19 January 2015|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150119204215/http://www.peyab.org/maruneng.htm#|archive-date=2015-01-19|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Marun Reservoir Dam|url=http://www.jtma.ir/en/projectlisten/damen/marunen|publisher=JTMA Co.|accessdate=19 January 2015}}</ref> | dam_height_thalweg = | dam_elevation_crest = | dam_width_crest = | dam_width_base = | dam_volume = {{Convert|9000000|m3|cuyd|abbr=on}} | spillway_count = | spillway_type = | spillway_capacity = | res_name = | res_capacity_total = {{Convert|1200000000|m3|acre.ft|abbr=on}} | res_capacity_active = | res_capacity_inactive= | res_catchment = | res_surface = {{Convert|25|km2|mi2|abbr=on}} | res_max_length = | res_max_width = | res_max_depth = | res_elevation = | res_tidal_range = | plant_name = | plant_coordinates = | plant_operator = | plant_commission = 2004 | plant_decommission = | plant_type = Conventional | plant_turbines = 2 x 75 [[megawatt|MW]] [[Francis-type]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Marun Dam and Power Plant|url=http://www.narvanarra.com/files/pdf/Marun_En.pdf|publisher=Narvan Arra|accessdate=19 January 2015}}</ref> | plant_hydraulic_head = | plant_capacity = 150 MW | plant_annual_gen = | website = | extra = }} '''Marun Dam''', also spelled '''Maroun''', is a rock-fill [[embankment dam]] on the [[Marun River]] about {{Convert|15|km|mi|abbr=on}} north of [[Behbahan]] in [[Behbahan County]], [[Khuzestan Province]], [[Iran]]. The dam serves to provide water for irrigation and to generate [[hydroelectric]] power as well. Construction on the dam began in 1989 and it was completed in 1998. A smaller Marun-II regulator dam is planned downstream.<ref>{{cite web|title=Marsh Draining Operations|url=http://www.amarfoundation.org/heritage/chapters/203.php|publisher=Amar International Foundation|accessdate=19 January 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313110759/http://www.amarfoundation.org/heritage/chapters/203.php|archivedate=13 March 2013|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=...]|first1=edited by L. Berga ... [Organised by Spanish National Committee on Large Dams - SPANCOLD|title=Roller compacted concrete dams : proceedings of the IV International Symposium on Roller Compacted Concrete (RCC) Dams, 17-19 November 2003, Madrid, Spain|date=2003|publisher=Balkema|location=Rotterdam [u.a.]|isbn=9058095649|pages=140-143|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=07w-L_OiFycC&pg=PA139&lpg=PA139&dq=marun+dam&source=bl&ots=0bY7VnmFc8&sig=QEYKCqK6yelX1tPru7qBPnGcr1g&hl=en&sa=X&ei=yF69VIahDcSHsQSm8YAY&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=marun%20dam&f=false|accessdate=19 January 2015}}</ref> The 150 MW power station was commissioned in 2004.<ref>{{cite web|title=130 MW Aras (Gara Chilar) Hydropower Plant|url=http://cdm.unfccc.int/filestorage/7/9/29V0UERN47YKXZ8GJWOMLIB13H6TDF.pdf/PDD.pdf?t=UW98bmlmeGU4fDA5iadekCb67sK_LPHbqHnQ|publisher=United Nations CDM|accessdate=19 January 2015|date=19 April 2013}}{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
